query:
SELECT 
                    id as "id!: Uuid", 
                    group_id as "group_id: Uuid",
                    template_name,
                    template_title,
                    ticket_title,
                    ticket_description,
                    created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>", 
                    updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
                   FROM task_templates
                   WHERE group_id = $1
                   ORDER BY template_title ASC
